      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_3083147129494672907.png",
                "key": "箱纸切削术",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "箱纸切削术"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span><br>生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">猫箱急件</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">安全运输护盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/e1d9ab13ba19969303b42dbee09f59e7_8455133479256327191.png",
                "key": "呜喵町飞足",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "呜喵町飞足"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>，在敌方场上生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猫草豆蔻</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/ec58f74c94bbd19ecbb0c33f972f5788_8432924077594289478.png",
                "key": "秘法·惊喜特派",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "秘法·惊喜特派"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span><span>]</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span><span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span><span>]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_8678217917234860333.png",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾<br></span></strong>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">猫箱急件</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绮良良为出战角色时，我方切换角色后：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，抓1张牌。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到2次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">安全运输护盾<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">护盾</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br></span>为我方出战角色提供2点护盾。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">猫草豆蔻</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所在阵营打出2张行动牌后：</span>对所在阵营的出战角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8688240247996076793.png",
